<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>고객만족팀 실적 모니터링 대시보드</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #f4f7fb;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .app {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .sidebar {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f5f9ff 100%);
      color: #0f172a;
      padding: 24px 18px;
      border-right: 1px solid #dbe7f5;
      box-shadow: 8px 0 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    .logo {
      margin-bottom: 34px;
      padding: 2px 0 6px;
    }

    .logo-img {
      width: 165px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .menu-title {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #64748b;
      margin: 26px 0 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .menu-item {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      color: #334155;
      font-size: 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: 0.2s;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .menu-item.active {
      background: #eaf2ff;
      color: #1d4ed8;
      border-color: #cfe0ff;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
    }

    .menu-item:hover {
      background: #f1f6ff;
      color: #1d4ed8;
    }

    .main {
      padding: 24px;
      overflow: auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .page-title h1 {
      font-size: 26px;
      letter-spacing: -0.8px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .page-title p {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .top-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .select,
    .input {
      height: 44px;
      border: 1px solid #dbe3ef;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 0 14px;
      outline: none;
      color: #334155;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .btn {
      height: 44px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 0 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #2563eb;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #1d4ed8;
    }

    .btn-light {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #dbe3ef;
      color: #334155;
    }

    .kpi-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .kpi-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    .kpi-card .label {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .kpi-card .value {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.8px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .kpi-card .change {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      padding: 5px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .up {
      background: #dcfce7;
      color: #15803d;
    }

    .down {
      background: #fee2e2;
      color: #b91c1c;
    }

    .neutral {
      background: #e0f2fe;
      color: #0369a1;
    }

    .dashboard-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5edf7;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card-header {
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #edf2f7;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .card-header h2 {
      font-size: 17px;
      letter-spacing: -0.4px;
    }

    .card-header p {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 5px 9px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .badge-blue {
      background: #dbeafe;
      color: #1d4ed8;
    }

    .badge-green {
      background: #dcfce7;
      color: #15803d;
    }

    .badge-orange {
      background: #ffedd5;
      color: #c2410c;
    }

    .badge-red {
      background: #fee2e2;
      color: #b91c1c;
    }

    .badge-gray {
      background: #f1f5f9;
      color: #475569;
    }

    .bar-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .bar-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 86px 1fr 56px;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .bar-name {
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #334155;
    }

    .bar-track {
      height: 12px;
      background: #edf2f7;
      border-radius: 999px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .bar-fill {
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2563eb, #38bdf8);
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .bar-value {
      font-weight: 900;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .operator-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .operator-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 42px 1fr auto;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 14px;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #38bdf8);
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .operator-info h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .operator-info p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .operator-score {
      text-align: right;
    }

    .operator-score strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .operator-score span {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .split-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .issue-list,
    .callback-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .issue-item,
    .callback-item {
      padding: 14px;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .issue-top,
    .callback-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .issue-top h3,
    .callback-top h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .issue-item p,
    .callback-item p {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    th,
    td {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #edf2f7;
      text-align: left;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    th {
      background: #f8fafc;
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    td {
      color: #334155;
    }

    .status-good {
      color: #15803d;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .status-warning {
      color: #c2410c;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .status-danger {
      color: #b91c1c;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .mini-chart {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(10, 1fr);
      align-items: end;
      gap: 8px;
      height: 180px;
      padding: 14px 4px 4px;
    }

    .chart-bar {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #60a5fa, #2563eb);
      border-radius: 10px 10px 4px 4px;
      min-height: 24px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .chart-bar span {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -24px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #64748b;
      white-space: nowrap;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .notice-box {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 15px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: #334155;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1400px) {
      .kpi-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }

      .split-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .dashboard-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .app {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .sidebar {
        display: none;
      }

      .topbar {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .top-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .select,
      .input,
      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .kpi-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .bar-row {
        grid-template-columns: 70px 1fr 50px;
      }

      table {
        display: block;
        overflow-x: auto;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="./비타브릿지_로고.png" alt="비타브릿지 로고" class="logo-img" />
      </div>

      <div class="menu-title">팀장 대시보드</div>
      <div class="menu-item active">고객만족팀 실적</div>
      <div class="menu-item">상담원별 현황</div>
      <div class="menu-item">콜백 관리</div>
      <div class="menu-item">민원/이슈 관리</div>

      <div class="menu-title">예약 운영</div>
      <div class="menu-item">예약 전환 분석</div>
      <div class="menu-item">검진센터 응대 현황</div>
      <div class="menu-item">기업별 문의 현황</div>
      <div class="menu-item">미처리 예약</div>

      <div class="menu-title">리포트</div>
      <div class="menu-item">일간 리포트</div>
      <div class="menu-item">주간 리포트</div>
      <div class="menu-item">상담 품질 평가</div>
    </aside>

    <main class="main">
      <section class="topbar">
        <div class="page-title">
          <h1>고객만족팀 실적 모니터링 대시보드</h1>
          <p>팀장이 상담 처리량, 예약 전환율, 콜백 미처리, 고객 이슈를 실시간으로 확인합니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="top-actions">
          <select class="select">
            <option>오늘</option>
            <option>최근 7일</option>
            <option>이번 달</option>
            <option>직접 선택</option>
          </select>
          <select class="select">
            <option>전체 상담원</option>
            <option>홍나현</option>
            <option>오태하</option>
            <option>남정민</option>
            <option>김승석</option>
            <option>이수정</option>
          </select>
          <button class="btn btn-light">엑셀 다운로드</button>
          <button class="btn btn-primary">리포트 생성</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="kpi-grid">
        <div class="kpi-card">
          <div class="label">총 인입콜</div>
          <div class="value">326</div>
          <span class="change up">▲ 12.4% 전일 대비</span>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi-card">
          <div class="label">응대 완료</div>
          <div class="value">294</div>
          <span class="change neutral">응대율 90.2%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi-card">
          <div class="label">예약 전환</div>
          <div class="value">118</div>
          <span class="change up">전환율 40.1%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi-card">
          <div class="label">미처리 콜백</div>
          <div class="value">17</div>
          <span class="change down">주의 필요</span>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi-card">
          <div class="label">평균 응대시간</div>
          <div class="value">4분 18초</div>
          <span class="change neutral">목표 5분 이내</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="dashboard-grid">
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h2>시간대별 인입콜 현황</h2>
              <p>상담 인력 배치와 피크타임 확인용</p>
            </div>
            <span class="badge badge-blue">실시간</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="mini-chart">
              <div class="chart-bar" style="height: 42%;"><span>09시</span></div>
              <div class="chart-bar" style="height: 58%;"><span>10시</span></div>
              <div class="chart-bar" style="height: 76%;"><span>11시</span></div>
              <div class="chart-bar" style="height: 64%;"><span>12시</span></div>
              <div class="chart-bar" style="height: 48%;"><span>13시</span></div>
              <div class="chart-bar" style="height: 85%;"><span>14시</span></div>
              <div class="chart-bar" style="height: 91%;"><span>15시</span></div>
              <div class="chart-bar" style="height: 73%;"><span>16시</span></div>
              <div class="chart-bar" style="height: 55%;"><span>17시</span></div>
              <div class="chart-bar" style="height: 30%;"><span>18시</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h2>상담원별 예약 전환율</h2>
              <p>상담 완료 건수 대비 예약 확정 비율</p>
            </div>
            <span class="badge badge-green">목표 38%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="bar-list">
              <div class="bar-row">
                <div class="bar-name">홍나현</div>
                <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 48%;"></div></div>
                <div class="bar-value">48%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bar-row">
                <div class="bar-name">오태하</div>
                <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 43%;"></div></div>
                <div class="bar-value">43%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bar-row">
                <div class="bar-name">남정민</div>
                <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 37%;"></div></div>
                <div class="bar-value">37%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bar-row">
                <div class="bar-name">김승석</div>
                <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 31%;"></div></div>
                <div class="bar-value">31%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bar-row">
                <div class="bar-name">이수정</div>
                <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 29%;"></div></div>
                <div class="bar-value">29%</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="dashboard-grid">
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h2>상담원별 실적 상세</h2>
              <p>팀장 코칭 및 업무 배분 판단용</p>
            </div>
            <span class="badge badge-blue">오늘 기준</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="operator-list">
              <div class="operator-item">
                <div class="avatar">홍</div>
                <div class="operator-info">
                  <h3>홍나현</h3>
                  <p>응대 72건 · 예약 35건 · 평균 3분 52초</p>
                </div>
                <div class="operator-score">
                  <strong>96</strong>
                  <span>품질점수</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="operator-item">
                <div class="avatar">오</div>
                <div class="operator-info">
                  <h3>오태하</h3>
                  <p>응대 63건 · 예약 27건 · 평균 4분 11초</p>
                </div>
                <div class="operator-score">
                  <strong>92</strong>
                  <span>품질점수</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="operator-item">
                <div class="avatar">남</div>
                <div class="operator-info">
                  <h3>남정민</h3>
                  <p>응대 58건 · 예약 21건 · 평균 4분 39초</p>
                </div>
                <div class="operator-score">
                  <strong>87</strong>
                  <span>품질점수</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="operator-item">
                <div class="avatar">김</div>
                <div class="operator-info">
                  <h3>김승석</h3>
                  <p>응대 49건 · 예약 15건 · 평균 5분 08초</p>
                </div>
                <div class="operator-score">
                  <strong>81</strong>
                  <span>품질점수</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h2>팀장 확인 필요 항목</h2>
              <p>미처리, 지연, 불만성 상담 우선 확인</p>
            </div>
            <span class="badge badge-red">7건</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="notice-box">
              <strong>오늘 주의 포인트</strong><br />
              ① 15시 이후 인입콜이 급증하여 평균 대기시간이 상승했습니다.<br />
              ② 콜백 미처리 17건 중 5건은 2시간 이상 지연되었습니다.<br />
              ③ 특정 검진센터의 대장내시경 마감 안내 관련 불만 문의가 반복되고 있습니다.<br />
              ④ 예약 전환율이 낮은 상담원은 패키지 설명 스크립트 점검이 필요합니다.
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="split-grid">
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h2>미처리 콜백</h2>
            <span class="badge badge-orange">17건</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="callback-list">
              <div class="callback-item">
                <div class="callback-top">
                  <h3>한지윤 · 010-4421-8891</h3>
                  <span class="badge badge-red">2시간 지연</span>
                </div>
                <p>검진센터 변경 요청. 오후 4시 이전 재연락 희망.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="callback-item">
                <div class="callback-top">
                  <h3>김도윤 · 010-7762-3310</h3>
                  <span class="badge badge-orange">확인 필요</span>
                </div>
                <p>기업 지원금 적용 여부 문의. 인사팀 확인 필요.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="callback-item">
                <div class="callback-top">
                  <h3>정민아 · 010-1145-9090</h3>
                  <span class="badge badge-gray">대기</span>
                </div>
                <p>수면내시경 가능 일정 재안내 요청.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
